beer.beer_name: Double Hazy - Double Hazy Mosaic IPA
beer.beer_description: A double-plus-good revelation of melon, tropical fruit and peach, the Double Hazy Mosaic IPA takes lush to a new level. Big-flavoured yet exceptionally balanced with just a hint of bitterness – from the first, silky sip through to the juicy finish – it’s one hell of a beer.
